messages.message: Hi all, is Scheduler an app that is meant for use? I’m getting this error when opening on prod. Seems fine on dogfood.

@Lee  - Scheduler is enabled only on dogfood. This is because we share the same database with the production.  To avoid multiple triggers happening because of shared databases we have disabled it in prod. There’s a current on going activity to separate the databases. Once that’s done we’ll enable it in prod as well.
